Subject: Legal -
Records Retention

By now each of you should have received a copy of Mr.
John Reilly's guidelines concerning our Records
Retention Program.

T£ you have not yet read and thoroughly understand
these guidelines, please do so inmediately.

I have attached a limited number of "Records Transfer
List" (RTL) for your use. If you need more, please
vequest them through Linda Martin in Greensboro.

I£ you have any questions, please let me know.

Dick
